author: Mark Manson
description:
In this video, I pull back the curtain on one of the most ambitious experiments I’ve ever attempted: trying to change a stranger’s life in a single night. Over four evenings with 30 complete strangers, I built a high-end, once-in-a-lifetime experience designed to break their patterns, crack open their assumptions, and push them into real vulnerability. From curated conversations to fire-walking, I tried every tool I’ve learned over twenty years of coaching to create meaningful, rapid transformation. Enjoy.

If you are not already a member of my premium community, get access to monthly challenges and daily action steps that add up to real change here: https://mrk.mn/ZcFwvxv

FREE: For practical advice each week that might change your life, sign up for my newsletter here: http://bit.ly/3JRg3NX

Oh yeah, and I’m Mark Manson, 3x #1 NY Times bestselling author of:
